message.content:
I need to identify the tax accrued but not yet paid from the balance sheet. This would typically be found in "Taxes Payable" line item under liabilities.

Looking at the balance sheet, I can see the "Taxes Payable" line:

| Account | Initial_amount | Initial_date | End_amount | End_date |
| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
| Taxes Payable | 0.00 | 2023-12-31 | 288001.20 | 2024-01-28 |

The initial value of Taxes Payable was 0.00 on 2023-12-31, and the end value was 288001.20 on 2024-01-28.

These are the tax amounts that have been accrued but not yet paid by the company.

```json
{"solution": {'initial value': '0.00', 'end value': '288001.20'}}
```
